data.description: In the desirable community of Clublands Antioch, this charming 5 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home boasts over 3,400 square feet of open living with an unfinished basement, which can be converted to fit your needs. Upon entering the home, you're welcomed into the two-story foyer with a spacious living area to the right. The home also features cathedral ceilings, ceramic tiling, a large eat-in kitchen, second level owner's bedroom with a walk-in closet and en suite bathroom, a cozy back deck, and a first level bedroom. The community offers amenities including walking trails, Homer White Lake, multiple playgrounds and is centrally located just a short drive to Raven Glen Forest Preserve, I-94, downtown Antioch and ample recreational options!
